# Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050


//Showing my name
### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/



### Get all books
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books

### Get book by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books/1

### Search by author 
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/books?author=Alex

### Searching by title 
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?title=Node




### Full-text q (title or author)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?q=node

### Create a new book
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hono by Denis",
  "author": "Wachira Denis",
  "description": "A book about Hono framework",
  "published": "2025-09-21",
  "pages": 127
}

### Update 
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hono by Wachira",
  "pages": 150
}

### Delete a book
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/7